Name: SokoFrog
About the game: SokoFrog is a puzzle game about pushing boxes, push the boxes in their proper places to get to the next level, but be careful where you push your box so you don't break it 100 levels. there are 5 different maps, each with its own play style. And 15 unlockable skins Controls: Directional keys : ⬆, ⬅, ⬇, ➡ / W, A, S, D / Gamepad: D-Pad Be careful with: Thorns: Water: Fall: Traps: Credits: Music: @graciettilive.
